About this item

  • Premium Man Made Upper
  • Premium insole provides arch support
  • Rubber slip resistant outsole
  • Relaxed fit

Description

Man made material that is lightweight and very flexible. The insole is made of a high density foam that contours to the foot with arch support and antimicrobial technology. Slip resistant rubber outsole adds to the stability for both oil and water surfaces. Shoe is lightweight making your feet feel fresh all day. Functional backstrap allows the shoe to be worn as a clog or sling back. Generous toe box leaves the foot feeling fresh all day long.
